profile:
We are a residentially focused rubber surfacing company aimed at adding safety and value to peoples' homes. We have experience installing wet pour rubber surfaces for over fifteen years.

***

Wet pour rubber surfacing originated in Europe, making its way to North America in more recent years. The product is familiarly found around playgrounds and splash pads. However we have seen the benefits of using this product and method to customize the exterior of homes. Wishing to continue wrapping old tired exteriors of homes to add safety and new life to the exterior environment of the property.

***

Paul and Matthew Bousfield are brothers that have been installing rubber surfaces since they were young teenagers. Growing up installing rubber every summer until they were through University and decided to begin their own business. They personally oversee and run all jobs to ensure the highest quality of workmanship on every installation.
